    <detaileddescription>
<para>This tutorial will cover creating two types of select menus:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>A generic select menu with just text</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>An auto-populated role select menu.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>This first example demonstrates creating a select menu, receiving select menu clicks, and sending a response message.</para>
